data.title: Top Mid Nebula + Market Star
data.description: Cover a push up Mid with these smokes, with the option to take back the star at Market for a more aggressive play.

data.title: B Site Wall Nebulas + Jump Up Pull
data.description: Use Nebula to block sight lines, with a pull to give your team a protected scale onto B Site. You can also smoke Spawn instead of Stairs, if you are looking to contest back site.

data.title: A Link Site Split Nebula Smokes
data.description: Block off sight lines with these Nebula lineups so you can cover your approach onto A Site.
